《'''从小李到老李 ：一个中国人的一生'''》({{lang-fr|'''''Une vie chinoise'''''}})是[[法国|法国]]漫画，作者们是{{link-fr|李昆武|Li Kunwu|李昆武}}和[[欧励行|欧励行]](Philippe Ôtié)，画插图者是李昆武，英文译者是Edward Gauvin。<ref name=SmithsonianAPA>"[http://smithsonianapa.org/bookdragon/a-chinese-life-by-li-kunwu-and-philippe-otie-translated-by-edward-gauvin/ A Chinese Life by Li Kunwu and Philippe Ôtié, translated by Edward Gauvin] {{Wayback|url=http://smithsonianapa.org/bookdragon/a-chinese-life-by-li-kunwu-and-philippe-otie-translated-by-edward-gauvin/ |date=20200502134932 }}." [[Smithsonian_Asian_Pacific_American_Center|Smithsonian Asian Pacific American Center]]. Retrieved on 13 February 2015.</ref> 

本漫画介绍李昆武的[[文化大革命|文化大革命]]生活。

